\p
\v 52 Unozvirumbidzireiko nezvakashata, iwe mhare? Tsitsi dzaMwari dziripo misi yose.
\p
\v 2 Rurimi rwako runofunga kutaura zvakaipa;
\s Rwakafanana nechisvo chinopinza, ruchiita zvinonyengera.
\p
\v 3 Unoda zvakaipa kupfuura zvakanaka;
\s Nokureva nhema kupfuura kutaura zvakarurama.
\p
\v 4 Unoda mashoko ose okuparadza, Iwe rurimi runonyengera.
\p
\v 5 Mwari achakuparadzawo saizvozvo nokusingaperi,
\s Achakubata akakubvisa patende rako,
\s th(ukudzura panyika yavapenyu.
\p
\v 6 Vakarurama vachazviona vakatya, Vachamuseka, vachiti,
\p
\v 7 "Tarirai, hoyu munhu asina kuita Mwari nhare yake,
\s Asi akavimba nokuwanda kwepfuma yake,
\s Akazvisimbisa pazvakaipa zvake."
\p
\v 8 Asi kana ndirini, ndakafanana nomuorivhi munyoro muimba yaMwari;
\s Ndinovimba netsitsi dzaMwari nokusingaperi-peri.
\p
\v 9 Ndichakuvongai nokusingaperi, nokuti
\s ndimi makazviita;
\s Ndichamirira zita renyu pamberi pavatsvene
\s venyu nokuti rakanaka.
